Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.40,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}如伊卡洛斯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:40.03,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}那份纯真的勇气如今已不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.38,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.75,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}将那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:47.79,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}平凡无奇地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:52.45,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}怀着无数问号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:03:00.27,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}寻找答案 却陷入迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:07.67,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}若能得知 答案的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:14.24,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}一切将化作崭新的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.79,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这阵风的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:22.48,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}定会有真实的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.39,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:27.00,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这些泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:30.59,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}总有一天会干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:36.69,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:41.83,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:45.88,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}只需微微一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:48.59,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}便能迎着清风 乱了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:52.58,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be1}勇往直前吧
