Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:50.94,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}纷纷雪花 是星星的碎屑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:55.13,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}将手伸向天体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:59.20,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}你也感受到那交错的心愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:08.74,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,600)\blur4}此刻一切都在黑白之间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:20.60,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}悄悄溢出的白色气息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:24.77,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}那是心中话语的轮廓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:28.89,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定是那一点点温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:33.47,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}让天空撒下一线光明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:37.42,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(100,200)\blur4}悲痛伤感沾湿的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:41.32,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}为保持纯白重新合上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:49.62,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,500)\blur4}我有去面对未来那种温柔的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:54.12,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}在谁都不知道的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:58.32,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}等待黎明的鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:02.12,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}给我带来了光的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:06.49,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,300)\blur4}从明天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:11.02,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}纷纷雪花 是星星的碎屑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:14.97,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}将手伸向天体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:18.82,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}你也相信那交错的心愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:28.42,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,500)\blur4}此刻一切都在黑白之间
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------EDCN1-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:32.70,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}当两人漂移不定的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:34.65,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}相互触碰之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:41.58,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻 你在想着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:47.31,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}隔着玻璃晃过的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:49.21,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那忧伤的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.55,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}距离那么近 却无法触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:23:00.02,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}积累种种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:02.87,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}逃避着现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:10.89,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那时几近崩溃的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:14.24,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻仿佛已能面对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.92,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Love in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:18.35,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}打开门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.47,0:23:21.83,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}前往有你的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:28.90,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}告诉你这份焦灼已久的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:30.58,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Feel my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:36.50,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}在你坦然露出笑容的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.59,0:23:40.05,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:43.85,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}会让我的泪水更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.95,0:23:49.25,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}You are my only shooting star
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------PREV------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是头一次坐邻桌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方同学也很近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过和他有点远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道拓人同学喜不喜欢卷心菜肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 暧昧的电波满天飞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里飞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 认真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就从实招了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 别生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 隔着玻璃可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这游戏不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 您真死板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚上任的班长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系嘛 反正隔着玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你是津名志拓人同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是渡边加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴能坐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 隔着玻璃可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要说的话应该是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 事先声明一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种结婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我是人妻女高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请叫我渡边太太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相亲相爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤须方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是隔着玻璃可以的人么？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车轮 是车轮 巨大的车轮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs22}（就这里）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本该为我所用的巨大车轮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要将我碾过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年级的远藤沙里奈部长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是津名志拓人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临「夜间飞行」戏剧社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位已经认识了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年级的山姿·Jaguar学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样1年级的姿目·Tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我学姐 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 别在学校叫我少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 副部长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副部长？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有美少年的气场嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站上台会很打眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说…你可以驾驶素体（Cybody）？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是印记？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是什么伤痕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}（兴趣十足）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕和印记重叠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是前所未闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有许多疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚为了保护和子而战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白马王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人为什么会绑架她？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得昨晚驾驶素体时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围的世界是什么样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入了很奇异的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 素体只能在那奇异的空间活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体活动时 世界的时间会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前 素体只能在那零时空间里活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在普通时空中只不过是普通的巨大人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果它在普通时空中也能活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能从军事 政治乃至经济上改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀有这种企图的人 就在这岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戏剧社啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团 第2队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放逐时代（Banishing Age）代表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团 第3队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九重葛（Bougainvilleae）代表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团 第4队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成人银行（Otona Bank）代表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团 第5队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芯（Filament）代表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猩红之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团 第6队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学协会（Kagaku Guild）代表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格林教授
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团总会 现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我们解开了气多巫女的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入了第二阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于使用电气柩启动了素体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这值得庆贺的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的试炼也同时降临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是本尊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实是他乘上了素体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何是第三阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那陌生的素体Tauburn（印）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还破坏了同志的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 芯的擅自行动也是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除皆水巫女的封印还为时过早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手下成员失控实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁眼说瞎话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该向猩红之吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该追究芯本身的责任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来追究？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在虽然是海德进行指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他并非支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过组织总需要领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今宵我有个提案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说敌性素体是不可容忍的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能击破那架讨厌的Tauburn 就可成为领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行指挥直至启程之日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐我等以荣光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐银河美少年以破灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事和必须做的事一致时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能听见世界的声音…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是 人生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就是男生入浴时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密入口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一年级生很流行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔着玻璃的KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽掉玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽掉玻璃做隔着玻璃的KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是单纯的亲嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍长…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又穿泳衣翻100次单杠去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看了银河美少年的美臀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让治怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己关在屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alephist（牛）被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加驭星者的资格也被剥夺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落也难免
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙才没那么纤细
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这么完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为他…报仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对上就能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不用这么急
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点亮希望之光的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正是我们「芯」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长认为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人是他们的间谍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能断定？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人他不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副部长喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这可是在说正事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们终于开始直接盯上和子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有资格驯化最强素体的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不作为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不让他做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的…和其他不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呵护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩的婚约关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 好风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南十字学园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好春天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶 耶 耶 耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(450,0)\fs23}（清纯？）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猩红之吻的第一阶段是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制和她KISS的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的心其实早已属于进藤须方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不善等待 是年轻人之常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会立刻行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜也无法入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼妹妹 陪我聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊天？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长 干姜水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎么想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可能就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为对付他们到这座岛上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事别说得这么草率
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思啊 他这人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经预料到外界也有驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和他们毫无干系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个有正义感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也要继续战斗就是另一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快转校为好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星一旦动真格 毫无胜算？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他火热地恋上在海边邂逅的那位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 恋爱故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思的故事 鱼妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年是位老练的渔师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫…萨姆如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆 好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年萨姆梦见自己与邂逅的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人乘着小船在银河中旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆恋上的是那位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是银河的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的冒险仍在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启 电气柩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去遛遛 Tetorioht（轮）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨嗨嗨 快登机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让今晚的我等太久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的小嘴了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没隔玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我先破了皆水巫女的封印吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn（印）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少扑腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒打出头钉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好身手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三阶所赐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人不忍心糟蹋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子不是门外汉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们休想再为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不许再碰岛上的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会像昨晚那样了 银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气力一亿伏！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讨厌清纯的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's a pinch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手 哲哉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们「芯」点亮着绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏惧时更应该全力一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无畏惧 前进是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填满银河
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tau之光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸裂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tau银河光束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的出头钉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打也会出头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的仇 我会报
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的肚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.59,0:22:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辣白菜卷 蛋包饭和蛤肉羹
Comment: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.84,0:23:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫穷是青春的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有生活费
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 pinch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漂亮人妻女高生家里？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.33,0:24:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成人银行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的银河 必会闪耀！
